        <mxCell id="s2_label" value="&lt;b&gt;SCENARIO 2: Agent A2 — ISOLATE (Cùng Group A! Policy per-agent, không per-group)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Step 1-3 giống A1 (cùng group → cùng cascade + merge → 8 entries). KHÁC ở Step 4: Policy!&lt;/i&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=13;fontColor=#b71c1c;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
